title: Billy Eichner Returns
description:
Actor and comedian Billy Eichner feels over the moon about being Conan O’Brien’s friend.


 

Billy sits down with Conan once again to discuss making an authentic gay romcom with Bros, taking control of his own career amidst a changing culture, and what he owes to the iconic Joan Rivers. Later, Conan wallows in distress over his wife’s healthy grocery selection.


 


 

Got a question for Conan? Call our voicemail: (323) 451-2821.


 

For Conan videos, tour dates and more visit TeamCoco.com.
